  "name": "Miraculous Possibility",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Your deity empowers you to perform minor miracles, allowing you to readily adapt to the fluctuating needs of your duties.</p>\n<p>Once during your daily preparations, you can use a spell slot to hold sheer divine potential, rather than using it to prepare a spell. You can use this spell slot to cast any spell you know from the divine spell list that's at least 2 levels lower than the slot you designate. The spell acts in all ways as a spell of 2 levels lower.</p>\n<p>You don't have any particular spell prepared in that slot until you cast it.</p>"
